**Structured extraction from unstructured text:**

```java
// Target: extract this from any salary slip text:
public record SalarySlipExtract(
    String applicantName,
    String employer,
    long monthlyGrossIncomePaise, // in paise for precision
    String employmentDate,        // ISO: yyyy-MM-dd
    int extractionConfidence      // 0-100: AI's self-reported confidence
) {}

@Service
public class SalarySlipExtractor {
    private final ChatClient chatClient;
    private final BeanOutputConverter<SalarySlipExtract> converter;

    public SalarySlipExtractor(ChatClient.Builder builder) {
        converter = new BeanOutputConverter<>(SalarySlipExtract.class);
        chatClient = builder
            .defaultSystem("""
                Extract salary slip details precisely.
                Convert amounts to paise (₹1 = 100 paise).
                Use ISO date format (yyyy-MM-dd) for dates.
                If a field is not found, use null.
                Rate your extraction confidence 0-100.
                """)
            .build();
    }

    public SalarySlipExtract extract(String salarySlipText) {
        String response = chatClient.prompt()
            .user(u -> u.text("""
                Extract the following from this salary slip:
                {format}

                SALARY SLIP TEXT:
                {text}
                """)
                .param("format", converter.getFormat())
                .param("text", salarySlipText))
            .call()
            .content();
        return converter.convert(response);
    }
}
```

